snippet: The Slovenian skier, who won two golds at the Sochi Olympics but struggled all through the World Cup season, has won three times so far this season, all in different disciplines.
lead_paragraph: The Slovenian skier, who won two golds at the Sochi Olympics but struggled all through the World Cup season, has won three times so far this season, all in different disciplines.

headline.main: Tina Maze Puts Chaotic Year Behind and Dominates Again
